Judul: DESIGN OF A FOUR-STROKE SINGLE-CYLINDER MOTOCROSS ENGINE
Abstrak:
This master’s thesis deals with the design of a four-stroke single-cylinder motocross
engine up to 250ccm. The content of the theoretical part is a review of three
contemporary motocross engines. The practical part deals with the conceptual
design of the engine itself, including the design in CAD software.
Kata Kunci: Engine, motocross, motorcycle, single-cylinder, four-stroke, design, Creo Parametric
